By end-user, the academic and research institutes segment accounted for the highest revenue-grossing segment in 2023, while the hospitals segment is predicted to grow at the fastest CAGR during the forecast period. Key market players include Roche Holding AG, Eli Lilly and Company, Biogen Inc., AbbVie Inc., Amgen Inc., Quest Diagnostics Incorporated, Siemens Healthineers, GE Healthcare, Cortechs Labs, and Avid Radiopharmaceuticals.

The report provides market analysis and forecast by type, diagnostic technique, and end-user, as well as by region, including North America, Europe, Asia Pacific, Latin America, and Middle East & Africa. The report also provides exhaustive company profiles of the top 10+ major market players and competitor analysis.
